Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:10.89,Top,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san!}Yuuri nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:12.79,Top,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What is it, Gojouin?}Có chuyện gì, Gojouin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:16.10,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Have you made any progress \Nwith your maid since last time?}Từ đợt đó có tiến triển gì chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:28.57,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I haven't told Gojouin anything \Nafter the help she gave me.}Mình đã không nói gì với cậu ấy từ sau hôm đó nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:33.32,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I was able to tell Lilith that I love her.}Tớ đã có thể nói ra tớ yêu Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.43,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Finally!}Cuối cùng thì!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:37.31,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{It finally happened!}Cuối cùng thì đã nói!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.22,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Congratulations!}Chúc mừng cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:39.86,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:40.93,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{And then?}Thế sau đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.96,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{And then what happened?}Sau đó thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.14,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{What did she say?}Cô ấy nói gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.79,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{What are your plans now?}Từ giờ cậu tính sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:50.17,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I imagine things must have \Nchanged quite a bit since then!}Tớ nghĩ nhiều chuyện phải thay đổi lắm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What's changed?}Thay đổi á?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.62,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{We have a new member of the family.}Chúng tớ có thêm thành viên gia đình.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.74,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I see. So that's what you meant.}Ý cậu là thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:17.94,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:21.24,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{The mansion's been quite a \Nbit livelier, thanks to her.}Nhờ vậy mà dinh thự đỡ yên ắng hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:24.43,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But it seems she doesn't \Nthink very highly of me.}Nhưng có vẻ không đánh giá tớ cao lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.24,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Does she really not?}Không hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:29.50,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I want to be friends with Natsume, though.}Nhưng tớ cũng muốn làm bạn với Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:34.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She loves Lilith, too, after all.}Vì cô ấy cũng yêu Lilth nữa mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:44.52,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{That is most definitely... a rival in love!}Đó chính là... đối thủ tình yêu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.16,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{So cold...}Lạnh quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.82,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What's taking that brat so long?}Thằng nhãi đó làm gì lâu thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.60,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Finally, he's here.}Ra rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.66,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Who's that?}Ai kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.51,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{W-Wait...}K-không lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.52,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Does he have a secret girlfriend, \Neven though she said she loves Lilith?}Có bạn gái bí mật dù đã nói yêu Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.92,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I will never approve of this!}Không thể chấp nhận được!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:11.64,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I should definitely take Lilith home!}Quả nhiên mình nên dẫn Lilith về!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:17.91,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{She's a necessary part of any love story!}Không lẽ là mảnh ghép cần có cho câu chuyện tình yêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:23.65,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{This is the kind of messy drama that I love!}Quả đúng là thể loại drama tớ cần hít.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:28.08,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{A former love and a new love...}Tình yêu cũ và tình yêu mới...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.03,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{A damsel's heart wavering between the two...}Trái tim thiếu nữ dao động...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:33.62,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yes! More of this!}Tuyệt! Quá tuyệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:37.88,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{This is getting fun!}Tớ hứng thú lên rồi đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:40.15,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Young lady, I've come to pick you up.}Cô chủ, mau về thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.36,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{We're leaving.}Đi nhanh nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.00,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{But it was just getting good!}Đang đến đoạn hay mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:57.50,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{W-Wasn't that the one famous for being \Nthe worst student at the academy,}N-Người đó... từng là học sinh cá biệt nhất học viện mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.07,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Fujisaki-senpai?!}Chị Fujisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.74,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Oh, no!}Chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.54,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What if she thinks I'm \Npicking a fight with her?}Nếu chị ta kiếm chuyện thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:06.80,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.13,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,V-Vâng?{Y-Yes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:10.04,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{How may I help you?}C-Có chuyện gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.77,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I haven't seen anything.}Em không thấy gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.63,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What are you doing out here?}Cô làm gì ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.65,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I'm here to take you home.}Tôi đến đón cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:25.49,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Oh. She's just a classmate?}Chỉ là bạn cùng lớp à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:28.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What else would she be besides a classmate?}Chứ ngoài ra còn gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:30.95,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Y-You're still a kid. \NYou don't need to know yet.}C-Cậu còn nhỏ nên chưa cần biết đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:36.96,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Anyway, why did you come today?}Vậy hôm nay sao cô đến đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:40.67,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Well, y'know...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.49,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{It's because I'm thinking \Nof going home soon.}Tôi nghĩ mình sắp về.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.67,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{So I just wanted to say goodbye.}Nên muốn đến chào tạm biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:49.03,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Oh... You're leaving?}Vậy cô về à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.11,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Gonna be lonely?}Có buồn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.10,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I won't be lonely.}Không hẳn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.84,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You're such a brat.}Chẳng dễ thương gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.30,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{S-So, anyway...}T-Thế nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.51,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{It's Christmas soon, right?}Cũng sắp Giánh Sinh rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.78,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Do you know what Lilith wants?}Cậu biết Lilith thích gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:05.53,Main,Guy A,0,0,0,,{Hey.}Này.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.28,Main,Guy A,0,0,0,,{Watch where you're going.}Mày có nhìn đường không đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.67,Main,Guy B,0,0,0,,{Damn it.}Chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:11.17,Main,Guy B,0,0,0,,{You'd better pay.}Đền đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:13.80,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{He's getting himself in trouble!}Sao lại dính vô rắc rối thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:17.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You were the ones who bumped into me.}Mấy người va trước mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.79,Main,Guy B,0,0,0,,{S-Say that again!}N-Nói gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:23.42,Main,Guy B,0,0,0,,{Do you have proof that we bumped into you?}Có bằng chứng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.74,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There's no proof that I \Nbumped into you, either.}Thế có bằng chứng gì tôi tông phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.64,Main,Guy A,0,0,0,,{Damn brat...}Thằng nhãi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:29.47,Main,Guy A,0,0,0,,{Do you know who you're dealing with?!}Mày đùa với bọn tao à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:37.58,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Aren't you embarrassed, \Ngetting so mad at a kid?}Đánh con nít không thấy xấu hổ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.37,Main,Guy A,0,0,0,,{Huh? This is none of your business. Piss off!}Hả? Liên quan gì, bỏ ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.03,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Hm?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.32,Main,Guy B,0,0,0,,{Th-That's not what we...}B-Bọn tôi không có ý...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:48.71,Main,Guy A; Guy B,0,0,0,,{We're sorry!}Rất xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:50.45,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Hey.}Này.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:54.71,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You talked back to those high schoolers.}Cậu trả treo với cả học sinh cấp 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.58,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Good going.}Ghê đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:59.91,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{But don't put yourself in too much danger.}Nhưng đừng làm mấy chuyện nguy hiểm nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.30,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You'll make Lilith worry.}Lilith sẽ lo lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.62,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're right. Sorry.}Phải nhỉ, xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.68,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks for helping me.}Cảm ơn vì đã giúp tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:10.46,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You were awesome, Natsume.}Cô ngầu lắm đó Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.81,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{It was nothing.}Có gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:15.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I know! Let me do something to thank you.}Phải rồi! Để tôi đãi cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.06,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Huh? Thank me?}Hả? Đãi tôi á?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.69,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I don't need that.}Không cần đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:19.82,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why not?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:22.28,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You saved me from getting into trouble.}Thì cô cứu tôi khỏi bọn họ mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.98,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{So I want to thank you.}Nên phải cảm ơn chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:27.39,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I don't know what to say to that.}Chuyện đó... tự nhiên lại nói thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.83,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Okay...}Thế thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:33.30,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{There's something I want \Nyour help with, then.}Có chuyện cần cậu giúp đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:39.83,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:43.01,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Did you go out to pick up the young master?}Cô đi đón chủ nhân hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:45.59,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I figured why not, for a change.}Ừm, thỉnh thoảng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:49.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You could have told me, then.}Vậy thì phải nói tôi chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.90,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Well, we'd better get going.}Vậy thôi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.44,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Let's go, Natsume.}Đi nào Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.12,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{R-Right.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:05.64,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Something seemed off about those two.}Bọn họ có gì đó kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.23,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{How many times do I have to tell you?!}Đã nói bao nhiêu lần rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:10.54,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What?! This is obviously the better one!}Hả? Cái này tốt hơn mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:11.97,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No, no!}Không không!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:16.09,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith's childlike charm is part \Nof what's so attractive about her!}Sự trẻ con của Lilith cũng là điểm quyến rũ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.82,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{No freaking way!}Nói gì thế hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:23.99,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{It's her grown-up, \Nmature side that's so awesome!}Lilith phải theo phong cách người lớn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:31.57,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm glad they're getting along better.}Bọn họ thân thiết với nhau là tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:34.94,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is something the matter?}Có gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:36.69,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Er, no.}À không.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.39,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Anyway, I'm not here to argue with you.}Tóm lại tôi không đồng ý với cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:43.83,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You said you wanted me to \Nhelp you choose a gift.}Cô nói muốn tôi giúp chọn quà mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.58,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{So anyway, back to our discussion.}Tóm lại là tiếp tục chuyện lúc nãy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:52.34,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{A surprise?}Bất ngờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.41,Flashback - Sus Maid,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:56.99,Flashback - Sus Maid,Natsume,0,0,0,,{We're putting together a Christmas \Nparty without telling Lilith.}Chúng ta sẽ tổ chức tiệc Giáng sinh mà không nói Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.58,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why is it a secret?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.47,Flashback - Sus Maid,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Isn't it obvious?}Còn hỏi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:04.08,Flashback - Sus Maid,Natsume,0,0,0,,{We're going to keep it a secret, \Nand surprise her on the day of.}Chúng ta giữ bí mật và làm Lilith bất ngờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:07.46,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That makes sense.}Ý hay đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.62,Flashback - Sus Maid,Natsume,0,0,0,,Quyết định thế nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:18.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm going to tell Lilith that I've been \Ninvited to Gojouin's Christmas party.}Tôi đã nói Lilith mình đến nhà Gojouin ăn tiệc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:23.27,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{And I'm going to take her out, then bring \Nher back to the mansion in time.}Còn tôi dẫn cô ấy ra ngoài, câu giờ cho cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:28.08,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{That way, I can figure out what \Nshe wants while we're out, too.}Thế này thì vừa có thể đi chơi riêng hai người.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.71,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Two birds with one stone.}Một mũi tên trúng 2 chim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:37.39,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{O-Oh, yeah, Christmas is coming up soon, huh?}À hình như sắp Giáng sinh nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.66,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It is.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.66,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's hard not to be excited about \NChristmas, for some reason.}Tự nhiên cảm thấy hồi hộp ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.80,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, about our plans for the day...}Chủ nhân, về kế hoạch hôm đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:49.75,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Sorry, Lilith, I've been invited to \Na party at Gojouin's for Christmas.}Xin lỗi Lilith, tôi được Gojouin mời đến nhà rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is that true, young master?}Thật ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:55.85,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.93,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm going to be having \Ndinner at her place, too.}Tôi được mời dùng bữa tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.65,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:06.53,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{L-Lilith, why don't the two of \Nus go out on Christmas, then?}L-Lilith, hai chúng ta đi đón giáng sinh nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:08.83,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Okay. Thank you.}Ừm, cảm ơn cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:14.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, please enjoy \NGojouin-sama's party.}Chủ nhân, hãy vui vẻ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:16.28,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:31.31,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I need to at least give him a present.}Ít nhất cũng phải tặng quà cho chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:37.74,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\fs12\an5\c&H285E68&\3c&H9BBCC4&\shad0\pos(184.666,294.667)}{Atel\N\NAcademy}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.73,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Is what you just said true?}Chuyện đó là thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:40.31,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Would you and—}Ừm, nếu được thì cậu--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:42.94,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{By all means, I'd love to join!}Tớ rất muốn tham gia đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.06,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She's so close.}Gần quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.22,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{A Christmas surprise...}Tiệc giáng sinh bất ngờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.11,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{That's a great idea!}Ý tưởng hay đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:51.52,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I've read plenty of books on the subject.}Tớ đã đọc rất nhiều sách về nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:56.03,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{First, you're going to need \Nto do something romantic.}Đầu tiên cần gì đó lãng mạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.53,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{A helicopter ride for a \Nview of the nightscape...}Một chiếc trực thăng chở đi ngắm cảnh đêm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.71,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Rent out a ship for a dinner cruise...}Thuê một nhà hàng sang trọng...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.98,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{And the finale is in a bathroom with \Nrose petals floating in the bathtub,}Và cuối cùng là phòng tắm với hoa hồng nổi trên.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.52,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{candles to set the mood,}Thêm nến để tạo khung cảnh,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:13.79,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{and a Chambery and Christmas cake toast!}và bánh ngọt cùng sâm panh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:18.34,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Then the two share words of love, and...}Sau đó thì cả hai chim chuột nhau và...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:22.87,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I-I don't think I get it, but thanks.}T-Tớ không hiểu lắm nhưng cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:29.09,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, I lost control of myself.}Xin lỗi, tớ hơi mất kiểm soát.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:32.07,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{So, what exactly are your plans?}Vậy kế hoạch là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:36.05,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Actually, I wanted to \Ntalk to you about that.}Thực ra tớ muốn nói chuyện đó với cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:41.50,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Are you really going to \Nbe all right on your own?}Cậu đi một mình ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:43.00,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'll be fine.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:46.64,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I've been to Gojouin's house lots \Nof times. I know how to get there.}Tôi đã đến bao nhiêu lần rồi, dĩ nhiên là nhớ đường.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.08,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.40,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{C-Come on, Lilith.}T-Thôi nào Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.87,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You heard him.}Cậu ta có còn nhỏ nữa đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:53.85,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:58.80,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Please be sure to contact me if you \Nneed anything, okay, young master?}Chủ nhân, nếu có chuyện gì thì hãy liên lạc nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.78,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Got it.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:08.06,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That about does it for the first mission.}Đã xong nhiệm vụ đầu tiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.12,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Now we just...}Giờ thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.61,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Where's the target?}Mục tiêu đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.89,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{We've successfully taken her out.}Đã thành công đưa ra khỏi nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.20,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Hello, Fujisaki-san.}Chào cô, Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.27,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Good day.}Chào cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:30.18,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{My young lady has informed \Nme of the situation.}Tiểu thư đã nói cho tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.71,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{With respect, I will be directing the party.}Tôi sẽ nhận trách nhiệm tổ chức.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.71,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Do I have permission from the both of you?}Hai người có bằng lòng không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:38.21,Main,Yuuri; Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yes. Please and thank you.}Ừm, nhờ cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.00,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Then, first, young lady...}Đầu tiên tiểu thư...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.69,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Okay! Tell me what to do!}Tôi phải làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:50.85,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Why am I the one making the decorations?!}Tại sao tôi phải ngồi đây làm đồ trang trí?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:52.86,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Done.}Xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.12,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Indeed.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.96,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Now we just need to decorate it, and it's done.}Giờ trang trí nữa là xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.69,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-sama, please hold still for a moment.}Cậu có thể đứng yên không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.84,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Pardon me.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.31,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{You had some whipped cream on your nose.}Trên mũi cậu có dính kem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.89,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're very thoughtful, Fujisaki-san.}Cô tốt bụng thật đó, Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:14.72,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{No, I'm just used to doing these \Nkinds of things for the young lady.}Không, chỉ là tôi quen việc này thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.71,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{The young lady is rather clumsy.}Cô chủ rất hậu đậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.24,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I have to keep an eye on her, or...}Nên tôi phải luôn quan sát...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.29,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Is something the matter?}Có chuyện gì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:25.02,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No, I just realized the two of \Nyou really do love each other.}Không, chỉ là hai người thực sự yêu quý nhau nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:26.78,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{L-Love?}Y-Yêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.10,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I kind of envy you.}Ghen tị ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:36.89,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I'm confiscating this.}Tịch thu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:41.17,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{But it's such a rare pairing!}Nhưng hiếm lắm mới có bức chụp chung mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:46.95,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Making memories to keep is important, isn't it?}Tạo nên kỉ niệm cũng quan trọng lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.42,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah, it is.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.04,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Hey, Fujisaki...}Nè Fujisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:56.55,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I'd like to help cook, too.}Tôi cũng muốn nấu ăn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:04.05,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Then, young lady, could you please \Nput the strawberries on the cake?}Vậy thì tiểu thư hãy trang trí dâu tây lên bánh đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.64,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I can do that!}Tôi làm được!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:17.45,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{C-Crap...}N-Nguy quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:19.42,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I'm getting nervous.}Mình đang lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:22.66,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What are you supposed to talk \Nabout in these situation?}Phải nói gì trong tình huống này nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.68,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I know. I'll Kookle it.}Google xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.59,Main,Text,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs13\c&H353837&\3c&HF7FAF8&\shad0\pos(30,20)}{First time out together conversations\N}{\c&H84E178&\u1}{Conversations Can Make or Break a First Date\N Is It a Date if You Go Out Together? Conversation Expert Explains\NSigns That They like You Back}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:34.42,Main,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\an7\fs13\c&H353837&\3c&HF7FAF8&\shad0\pos(30,20)\c&H84E178&\u1}{Date Plans for Your First-Time Meeting\N No Conversation Topics? No Problem! Perfect Dating Spots\N [Relationship Quiz] Places to Go Before You're Going Steady}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:37.12,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{It's totally useless.}Chẳng có gì có ích cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:39.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is something the matter, Natsume?}Có gì sao, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:42.66,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Huh? No, uh...}À không...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:45.81,Main,Text,0,0,0,,{\an8\b1\c&H1A5C7F&\3c&HB1D7DF&\shad0\pos(72,75)\bord4}{Delicious\N}{\fnArial\fs30\c&HBEE9F2&\3c&H1B577C&}{Crêpes}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.53,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Let's have crêpes.}Ăn bánh crepe đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.18,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I'll go buy some.}Tôi đi mua.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.05,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Wait here, Lilith.}Chờ ở đây nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:55.19,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Natsume! You shouldn't run, or...}Natsume, đừng chay nhanh--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.56,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Are you all right?}Cô ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.56,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I-I'm fine.}O-Ổn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.71,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You aren't fine at all!}Ổn cái gì mà ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.53,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I look so stupid.}Trông mình cứ như con ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:12.61,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.77,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Dùng nó đi, tôi làm ẩm rồi.{Please use this. I soaked it in water.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:16.71,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.67,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{O-Okay.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:21.91,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Now's my chance.}Cơ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:25.81,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I need to apologize for my embarrassing \Nbehavior and for everything that's happened.}Phải xin lỗi vì hành vi đáng xấu hổ \Nkhi nãy và tất cả mọi chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.82,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{L-Lilith... About today—}L-Lilith, hôm nay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.27,Top,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you for everything \Nyou've done for me today.}Cảm ơn cô vì hôm nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:35.68,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You invited me out thinking \NI might be depressed, right?}Cô mời tôi vì thấy tôi có vẻ thất vọng nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:38.41,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I wasn't really...}Không hẳn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.31,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Are you okay with this, though?}Nhưng cô thấy ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:44.54,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{There must have been someone you \Nwanted to spend the day with.}Cô hẳn phải có người muốn ở bên cạnh nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.20,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{H-Huh?!}H-Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.75,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Why would there be?!}Làm gì có ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.68,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is that so?}Thế hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:53.68,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I saw the Christmas special in \Nthe magazine you were reading.}Tôi đã xem qua tạp chí Giáng sinh mà cô đọc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I thought there was someone \Nyou had feelings for.}Cứ tưởng có người thích rồi chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:59.56,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Th-That was y—}Đ-Đó là--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.69,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Never mind.}Bỏ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:09.02,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Let's enjoy the day, Natsume.}Natsume, hôm nay cùng tận hưởng nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.67,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Of course we will!}Dĩ nhiên rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm so glad.}May quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:27.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It looks good on you.}Trông hợp với cô lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:32.31,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{These cutesy things suit you better.}Mấy món này hợp với cô hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.12,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That's not true.}Không phải đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:36.47,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You're very cute, Natsume.}Cô dễ thương mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.68,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You're so embarrassing.}Xấu hổ quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.17,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.73,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You're welcome.}Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:50.24,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.38,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Lilith... I have something for you, too.}Lilith... đây là quà của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:54.60,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Here.}Tặng cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:58.08,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{May I open it?}Tôi mở ra được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:11.65,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I was planning to figure out what you\Nmight like and buy it today, but...}Thực ra tôi định hôm nay đi\N và hỏi xem cô thích gì rồi mua luôn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:17.40,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I'm thinking of going back \Nto the mansion soon.}Tôi nghĩ cũng chuẩn bị quay về...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:21.76,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{So you'd better use it to write \Nme a letter once in a while.}Thế nên thỉnh thoảng dùng nó viết thư cho tôi đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.49,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I will. I promise.}Ừm, tôi hứa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:33.96,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Natsume.}Cảm ơn Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.11,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.62,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I didn't think they'd keep it so dark.}Sao tối om vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.11,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Look at this, Lilith!}Đẹp quá Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.34,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:56.22,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Oh, no! Is she inside already?}Đã chạy vào trong rồi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:00.45,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Merry Christmas!}Chúc mừng giáng sinh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.84,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Huh? Lilith...}Hả? Lillith...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:05.29,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What about the surprise?}Bất ngờ đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.51,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What's going on?}Chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:09.74,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Sorry we didn't tell you.}Xin lỗi vì giấu cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:10.97,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{The truth is...}Sự thật là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.65,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.61,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What's the matter? It's soC late.}Có chuyện gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.29,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.60,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{So that's what you've \Nbeen doing with Natsume.}Ra đó là chuyện chủ nhân làm với Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:25.89,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:28.33,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{We wanted to surprise you.}Bọn tôi muốn làm cô bất ngờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:32.08,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But I couldn't keep a \Nsecret from you, Lilith.}Nhưng tôi không thể giấu Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:35.03,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I have to apologize to \NNatsume tomorrow, too.}Ngày mai tôi sẽ xin lỗi Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.27,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.78,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Sorry to bug you so late.}Xin lỗi vì làm phiền cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:45.47,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Just a moment, young master.}Chủ nhân, khoan đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:50.86,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I just came up with a great idea to \Nmake sure we don't disappoint Natsume.}Tôi vừa nghĩ ra 1 cách làm Natsume không buồn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:57.74,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{So I was the one who was being \Nsurprised, and you were...}Vậy người bất ngờ là tôi và cô...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:04.41,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with you?}Vậy là sao chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.65,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Are you all right?}Ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.83,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{F-Fujisaki-senpai?!}C-Chị Fujisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:12.54,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{H-H-H-Hello!}C-C-Chào chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.81,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Come on, Natsume-san.}Nào nào Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:17.97,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I'm sure you've got a lot to say.}Tôi biết có nhiều chuyện muốn nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:20.20,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Please come in.}Nên hãy vào nhà trước đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.42,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah, you should.}Ừm, phải đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.85,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Let's go, Natsume.}Đi thôi Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.93,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you for your help today.}Cảm ơn vì hôm nay nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.16,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Not at all.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:04.87,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{The young lady seems to \Nhave enjoyed it, as well.}Tiểu thư cũng có vẻ vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:09.85,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Fujisaki in a mini-skirt Santa outfit...}Fujisaki mặc váy ngắn Santa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:15.64,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Thank you for all your work today, Yuuri.}Hôm nay cậu cũng vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:19.84,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{I hope you'll continue being \Nyoung Tsukasa's friend.}Từ giờ hãy tiếp tục làm bạn với tiểu thư nhà tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:21.63,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Of course.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:24.49,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I hope you come by again, too, Fujisaki-san.}Cả cô cũng đến nữa nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.29,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Well, then...}Vậy thì tôi xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:41.37,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, you did fantastic today.}Chủ nhân, hôm nay thật là tuyệt nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:43.33,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks to you, too, Lilith.}Cô cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.37,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That was an impressive act.}Diễn đỉnh lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.21,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:53.80,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Did you pick out Natsume's \Nhair accessory, too?}Cô chọn kẹp tóc cho Natsume à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:54.80,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.72,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It suits her well, doesn't it?}Hợp lắm phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:57.72,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:59.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm sure she appreciated it.}Chắc cô ấy sẽ vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:03.90,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What about you, young master?}Còn chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:14.39,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith, how do I do this part?}Lilith, cái này làm sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:18.41,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Pass the needle under this knot.}Luồn kim qua nút thắt này.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.90,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I hope Natsume likes it.}Hi vọng Natsume thích nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:35.67,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes, I'm sure she will.}Nhất định rồi.
